overview:
The Outset Group
(Project Management, Business Analysis, and Leadership)

The Outset Group specializes in the staffing, training and consulting within the fields of project management, business analysis, and leadership. Our focus is Improving Project Management and Business Analysis Performance.

Our expertise in the fields of project management and business analysis allows us to deliver the very best talent available. We provide our candidates and clients with the guidance, and expertise to ensure the strength of their teams, alignment of their goals and delivery of successful projects through consulting, training and staffing services.

The Outset Group also offers individuals and teams the opportunity to learn and apply the most in demand management systems for project management and business analysis. We offer accredited, high impact training in the areas that define management excellence and enable success: Business Analysis, Project Management, Leadership, Communication, and Interpersonal Skills.

Work with an acknowledged leader and experience the benefits of our high impact, performance-oriented training. www.outsetgroup.com
